                                    <Property name="infoMessage" type="java.lang.String" value="&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Item event:&lt;/b&gt; Allows player to aquire items.&lt;br&gt;- X/Y: The position of the item event.&lt;br&gt;- Flag: The flag that is written when the item event is triggered (when the item is aquired).&lt;br&gt; - Flag Info: A helpful description of what the flag value refers to.&lt;br&gt;- Item: The item that is acquired by the event. Set to &quot;NOTHING&quot; for no item.&lt;br&gt;- Comment: Optional comment that is saved to the .asm file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;When an item row is selected:&lt;/b&gt; Left click will set the new X/Y position of the selected item event.&lt;/html&gt;"/>
                                    <Property name="model" type="com.sfc.sf2.core.models.AbstractTableModel" editor="org.netbeans.modules.form.ComponentChooserEditor">
